{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":0,"text":"The decorative use of wire in southern Africa"},{"time":3000,"text":"dates back hundreds of years."},{"time":5000,"text":"But modernization actually brought communication"},{"time":8000,"text":"and a whole new material, in the form of telephone wire."},{"time":12000,"text":"Rural to urban migration meant that newfound industrial materials"},{"time":17000,"text":"started to replace hard-to-come-by natural grasses."}]},{"cues":[{"time":21000,"text":"So, here you can see the change"},{"time":23000,"text":"from use -- starting to use contemporary materials."},{"time":25000,"text":"These pieces date back from the '40s to the late '50s."},{"time":30000,"text":"In the '90s, my interest and passion for transitional art forms"},{"time":34000,"text":"led me to a new form,"},{"time":36000,"text":"which came from a squatter camp outside Durban."}]},{"cues":[{"time":38000,"text":"And I got the opportunity to start working with this community"},{"time":42000,"text":"at that point, and started developing, really,"},{"time":45000,"text":"and mentoring them in terms of scale, in terms of the design."},{"time":51000,"text":"And the project soon grew from five to 50 weavers in about a year."},{"time":55000,"text":"Soon we had outgrown the scrap yards, what they could provide,"},{"time":59000,"text":"so we coerced a wire manufacturer to help us,"},{"time":62000,"text":"and not only to supply the materials on bobbins,"},{"time":65000,"text":"but to produce to our color specifications."}]},{"cues":[{"time":68000,"text":"At the same time, I was thinking, well,"},{"time":70000,"text":"there's lots of possibility here to produce contemporary products,"},{"time":74000,"text":"away from the ethnic, a little bit more contemporary."},{"time":78000,"text":"So I developed a whole range around -- mass-produced range --"},{"time":81000,"text":"that obviously fitted into a much higher-end decor market"},{"time":85000,"text":"that could be exported and also service our local market."}]},{"cues":[{"time":89000,"text":"We started experimenting, as you can see, in terms of shapes,"},{"time":93000,"text":"forms. The scale became very important,"},{"time":97000,"text":"and it's become our pet project. It's successful,"},{"time":101000,"text":"it's been running for 12 years. And we supply the Conran shops,"},{"time":105000,"text":"and Donna Karan, and so it's kind of great."}]},{"cues":[{"time":108000,"text":"This is our group, our main group of weavers."},{"time":111000,"text":"They come on a weekly basis to Durban."},{"time":113000,"text":"They all have bank accounts."},{"time":115000,"text":"They've all moved back to the rural area where they came from."},{"time":117000,"text":"It's a weekly turnaround of production."},{"time":119000,"text":"This is the community that I originally showed you the slide of."},{"time":123000,"text":"And that's also modernized today,"},{"time":125000,"text":"and it's supporting work for 300 weavers."},{"time":129000,"text":"And the rest says it all."}]},{"cues":[{"time":132000,"text":"Thank you very much."},{"time":133000,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}